TITLE: HANK III & ASSJACK - LIVE AT THE GATES OF HELL
Videographer: CuzN Wildweed

DESCRIPTION: A "best of" compilation of live clips of various
ASSJACK shows taped live at Alley Katz in Richmond, VA
from 2003 - 2006 and clips of 1 show from May 2005
at Bluecats in Knoxville, TN.
Special cameos by Dancing Outlaw Jesco White, Randy Blythe
from Lamb of God and Chris Arp from Psyopus.
